markets.title: Will Ethereum perform better than Bitcoin in 2024?
markets.subtitle: In 2024
markets.rules_primary: If Ethereum returns more than Bitcoin in 2024, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The values for the cryptocurrencies are taken by taking an average of the five minutes of CF Benchmarks' Bitcoin Real-Time Index (BRTI) and Ethereum Real-Time Index (ETHUSD_RTI) before any given time, excluding the top 20% and bottom 20% of values.
markets.early_close_condition: If this event occurs, the market will close the following 10:00 AM ET.
